00:16:36,264 --> 00:16:39,725
I mean, are we saying we should be legalizing crack?

245
00:16:40,385 --> 00:16:46,406
I mean, if we really did want to make the freeway ricks of the world go away, we would take away the earning potential, I guess, right?

246
00:16:46,426 --> 00:16:48,606
Yeah, by legalizing drugs and dropping the price.

