00:17:11,665 --> 00:17:14,928
Legalizing something like crack, there would definitely be trade-offs.

258
00:17:15,468 --> 00:17:17,590
Legalization would dramatically reduce crime.

259
00:17:18,631 --> 00:17:35,505
Obviously, the drug market crime would disappear and many drug-related crimes where it's sort of in the business economic compulsive crimes, that is crimes committed in order to pay for expensive illegal drugs, that would go down a lot too.

260
00:17:36,887 --> 00:17:38,108
What goes on the other side?

