00:23:33,418 --> 00:23:50,570
substitutes but they've worked very hard to make you think if you're an apple phone user that that is a special object of which there is no substitute and which apparently you will spend hundreds and hundreds and hundreds of dollars on one of my kids smashed my iphone yesterday.

